<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Template Email</title>
    <style>
      h1 {
        font-size: 18px;
      }
      body {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      }
      .container {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 1rem;
        height: 100vh;
        background-color: #f0f0f0;
      }
      .content {
        padding: 1rem;
        width: 70%;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <main class="container">
      <div class="content">
        <h1>Medical Check Up | PT Bank Mandiri</h1>
        <p>
          Hi <%= name %>!, <br />
          <br />
          Your Medical Check Up with Dr. Jane Doe at 09:00 on Monday, July 22, 2024 is scheduled.
        </p>
        <p><strong>Location:</strong> Jl. Jend. Sudirman No. 54, Jakarta Selatan, 12190</p>
        <p><strong>What to bring:</strong> Please bring your ID card</p>
        <p><strong>Notes:</strong> Come 15 minutes before the appointment time.</p>
      </div>
    </main>
  </body>
</html>
